title: Quran Viewer (dvd islam 911 cat stevens bible iraq pbs).
description:
Quran Viewer - version 2.9

"Quran Viewer" is a nice-looking and stable windows freeware that offers its user access to the "The Holy Quran" in 27 different languages (other than arabic).

It has been developed by "Jamal al-Nasir".

The languages for which there are more than 1 translation are : English (9) , German (2) , Spanish (2) , Urdu (2).

The languages for which there are 1 translation are : Alabanian, Azerbaijani, Bosnian, Chinese, Czech, Dutch, Finnish, French, Hausa, Indonesian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Malay, Malayalam, Maranao, Portuguese, Russian, Somali, Spanish, Swahili, Tamil, Thai, Turkish.

As I understand, "Multilingual Quran Viewer" is no longer being supported or developed since "Jamal al-Nasir" had to step down for personal reasons....So, cyber-dwellers : get it while you can !.
